FOODIE - Food Delivery Website 

Welcome to FOODIE, a modern, responsive, and interactive food delivery landing page website. This project is built using HTML, CSS, and modern JavaScript to deliver a smooth and engaging user experience for ordering delicious meals!

---

Features

1.Fully Responsive Design: Works beautifully on laptops, tablets, and mobile devices.
2. Interactive Ordering System:Users can click "Order Now" on any specific food category, and the website will automatically scroll them down and pre-fill the order form with their chosen meal!
3.Form Validation: Smart JavaScript checks if the user entered their name and phone number correctly before allowing them to place an order.
4. Smooth Scrolling: Clean navigation links that slide smoothly to different sections (`Home`, `Menu`, `About`, `Contact`).
5. Beautiful UI/UX:Warm and appetizing color palette with modern hover effects on buttons and images.

